Unitron:




"Brave words," Unitron said as he leapt back from Nightstrike's slashes, 
firing off ten two blasts from his rifle at him.  He ducked down to narrowly 
avoid Megatron's blast, and fired ten rapid optic blasts at the incoming 
Decepticon leader, digging his feet into the ground in case of impact.
